</li>
<li id="cite_note-:122-39"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-:122_39-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-:122_39-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-:122_39-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-:122_39-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-:122_39-4"><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFToribio2001" class="citation journal cs1">Toribio, Almeida Jacqueline (December 2001). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/bilingualism-language-and-cognition/article/abs/on-the-emergence-of-bilingual-codeswitching-competence/6C7726B73B05E63F2F9F304F027FBD48">"On the emergence of bilingual code-switching competence"</a>. <i>Bilingualism: Language and Cognition</i>. <b>4</b> (3): 203–231. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1017%2FS1366728901000414">10.1017/S1366728901000414</a>. <a href="/wiki/ISSN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISSN (identifier)">ISSN</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.worldcat.org/issn/1469-1841">1469-1841</a>. <a href="/wiki/S2CID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="S2CID (identifier)">S2CID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://api.semanticscholar.org/CorpusID:35047499">35047499</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Bilingualism%3A+Language+and+Cognition&amp;rft.atitle=On+the+emergence+of+bilingual+code-switching+competence&amp;rft.volume=4&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=203-231&amp;rft.date=2001-12&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.semanticscholar.org%2FCorpusID%3A35047499%23id-name%3DS2CID&amp;rft.issn=1469-1841&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1017%2FS1366728901000414&amp;rft.aulast=Toribio&amp;rft.aufirst=Almeida+J