<li id="cite_note-:6-45"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-:6_45-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-:6_45-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-:6_45-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-:6_45-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFGarcíaLeiboldBussCalandruccio2018" class="citation journal cs1">García, Paula B.; Leibold, Lori; Buss, Emily; Calandruccio, Lauren; Rodriguez, Barbara (19 September 2018). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6195050">"Code-Switching in Highly Proficient Spanish/English Bilingual Adults: Impact on Masked Word Recognition"</a>. <i>Journal of Speech, Language, and Hearing Research</i>. <b>61</b> (9): 2353–2363. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1044%2F2018_JSLHR-H-17-0399">10.1044/2018_JSLHR-H-17-0399</a>. <a href="/wiki/PMC_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="PMC (identifier)">PMC</a>&#160;<span class="id-lock-free" title="Freely accessible"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6195050">6195050</a></span>. <a href="/wiki/PMID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="PMID (identifier)">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/30076419">30076419</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Journal+of+Speech%2C+Language%2C+and+Hearing+Research&amp;rft.atitle=Code-Switching+in+Highly+Proficient+Spanish%2FEnglish+Bilingual+Adults%3A+Impact+on+Masked+Word+Recognition&amp;rft.volume=61&amp;rft.issue=9&amp;rft.pages=2353-2363&amp;rft.date=2018-09-19&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC6195050%23id-name%3DPMC&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F30076419&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1044%2F2018_JSLHR-H-17-0399&amp;rft.aulast=Garc%C3%ADa&amp;rft.aufirst=Paula+B.&amp;rft.au=Leibold%2C+Lori&amp;rft.au=Buss%2C+Emily&amp;rft.au=Calandruccio%2C+Lauren&amp;rft.au=Rodriguez%2C+Barbara&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC6195050&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACode-switching" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-:9-46"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-:9_46-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-:9_46-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-:9_46-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFHughesShaunessyBriceRatliff2006" class="citation journal cs1">Hughes, Claire E.; Shaunessy, Elizabeth S.; Brice, Alejandro R.; Ratliff, Mary Anne; McHatton, Patricia Alvarez (September 2006). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://journals.sagepub.com/doi/10.1177/016235320603000102">"Code Switching among Bilingual and Limited English Proficient Students: Possible Indicators of Giftedness"</a>. <i>Journal for the Education of the Gifted</i>. <b>30</b> (1): 7–28. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1177%2F016235320603000102">10.1177/016235320603000102</a>. <a href="/wiki/ISSN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISSN (identifier)">ISSN</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.worldcat.org/issn/0162-3532">0162-3532</a>. <a href="/wiki/S2CID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="S2CID (identifier)">S2CID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://api.semanticscholar.org/CorpusID:142565671">142565671</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Journal+for+the+Education+of+the+Gifted&amp;rft.atitle=Code+Switching+among+Bilingual+and+Limited+English+Proficient+Students%3A+Possible+Indicators+of+Giftedness&amp;rft.volume=30&amp;rft.issue=1&amp;rft.pages=7-28&amp;rft.date=2006-09&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.semanticscholar.org%2FCorpusID%3A142565671%23id-name%3DS2CID&amp;rft.issn=0162-3532&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1177%2F016235320603000102&amp;rft.aulast=Hughes&amp;rft.aufirst=Claire+E.&amp;rft.au=Shaunessy%2C+Elizabeth+